theme = ExtResource("3_snetv")
text = "The goal of the game is to prevent the baddies that spawn to the left from reaching the circle. Every baddy that enters the circle will cause you to lose health equal to their damage. 

Once your health reaches zero, or you're unable to kill a single baddy in a wave, it's game over!

"
