grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
theme = ExtResource("3_snetv")
text = "To stop the baddies from reaching their destination you can build towers using the buttons below.

You can place towers on any dirt space as long as it doesn't block the baddys from being able to reach the circle. 

Making a maze so that the baddies will take longer to reach their goal can be help ful, or you can Upgrade one tower to make it take on the whole wave.

Regardless of your strategy, as long as you kill at least one baddy in the wave and have life to spare, you'll complete the level.

The towers won't do anything on their own though. You'll need to build them up with tower mods."
autowrap_mode = 2

