offset_bottom = 209.0
grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
theme = ExtResource("3_snetv")
text = "That's right, Tower Mods! They're what you use to have your towers be more than a wall, and how you use them is up to you!

All mods come in three classes; Weapon, Power, or Aura. 

Weapon Mods shoot the baddies, pretty straight forward.

Power Mods supply power to the tower, more on them later.

Aura Mods provide passive buffs or debuffs, and their function depends on the tower it's a part of.

If an Aura Mod's tower has no weapon mods, then it will apply the buff/debuff to towers/baddies in it's range.

If a Weapon Mod is present in the tower, then instead the aura will only affect the mods of it's tower. In the case of debuffs these will be added to the weapon mod as an on hit effect.

"
autowrap_mode = 2

