grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
theme = ExtResource("3_snetv")
text = "If you insist!

All mods either have a power cost (Weapons and Auras) or power supply (Power) value. 

The only requirement for a tower to function is that their net power (the number in the button's centre) needs to be 0 or greater. Every point of power above 0 will increase that damage of weapon mods in that tower by 10%.

As a great man once said, with great power..."
autowrap_mode = 2

